# Elementor Widget Icons (eicons)

The value returned by `get_icon()` **must** be an eicon slug from this list.
Any other value leaves the widget without an image in the Elementor panel.

**Reference:** https://elementor.github.io/elementor-icons/

## Choosing an icon

Pick the icon that best describes the widget's purpose. Common picks:

| Widget type | Recommended icon |
|---|---|
| Steps / timeline / process | `eicon-time-line` |
| Carousel / slider | `eicon-carousel` |
| Posts / cards grid | `eicon-posts-grid` |
| Image + text box | `eicon-image-box` |
| Testimonial | `eicon-testimonial` |
| Call to action | `eicon-call-to-action` |
| Counter / number | `eicon-counter` |
| Accordion / toggle | `eicon-accordion` |
| Tabs | `eicon-tabs` |
| Icon box / info box | `eicon-info-box` |
| Heading / text | `eicon-heading` |
| Button | `eicon-button` |
| Divider | `eicon-divider` |
| Gallery | `eicon-gallery-grid` |
| Price table | `eicon-price-table` |
| Generic / fallback | `eicon-plug` |

